Powershell commands components: Cmdlets, Functions, Filters, Workflows
Cmdlet verbs: Get, Set, New, Add, Remove
Cmdlet Noun: Service, Process
New-ADUser -name -department
Pipeline: each console command line, 
          commands separated by '|', 
          commands execute from left to right
Object members: Properties/ Methods/ Events  --> 'Get-member'
To declare a variable: $name
To clear a variable: $name = $null
The script execution policy: 'Set-ExecutionPolicy -ExecutionPolicy (Restricted/AllSigned/ RemoteSigned/Unrestricted/Bypass)
          Restricted/AllSigned/ RemoteSigned/Unrestricted/Bypass
